    "starRating": "TWO",
    "comment": "Es necesario una ypf más. Aunque sea saliendo de Cafayate dirección a tucuman. A mi me tocó dos horas de fila, habían camionetas que tenían 3 bidones de 200 litros en la fila. Que quedaban media hora cargando. A mi parecer debería a ver una fila solo para esas camionetas, atrasan mucho.  Mal ahí YPF.\n\n(Translated by Google)\nWe need another YPF station. Even if it\u0027s just on the outskirts of Cafayate heading towards Tucumán. I had to wait in line for two hours; there were trucks with three 200-liter jerrycans in line, waiting half an hour to fill up. In my opinion, there should be a separate line just for those trucks; they cause a lot of delays. Shame on you, YPF.",
    "createTime": "2022-07-07T17:24:53.697546Z",
